OL,3,CNew MoT test centre faces further
OL,4,Cdelays
OL,6,FDrivers in Northern Ireland will have
OL,7,Fto wait even longer than expected for
OL,8,FMoT test backlogs to clear after a new
OL,9,Fvehicle test centre which was due to
OL,10,Fopen by the end of this year has once
OL,11,Fagain been delayed, UTV can reveal.
OL,13,FMoT vehicle testing centre at
OL,14,FHydebank, which was initially due to
OL,15,Fopen in 2022, was expected to begin
OL,16,Fbefore the end of this year.
