OL,3,CNew MoT test centre faces further
OL,4,Cdelays
OL,6,FThe hope had been that once the site
OL,7,Fis open, that it would help increase
OL,8,Fcapacity within the current vehicle
OL,9,Ftesting system and therefore reduce
OL,10,FMoT waiting times.
OL,12,FIt can now be revealed that the
OL,13,FDepartment for Infrastructure has
OL,14,F"served a notice to terminate its
OL,15,Fcontract" with a vehicle testing
OL,16,Fequipment company "with immediate
OL,17,Feffect".
OL,19,FThe department has said that the move
OL,20,Fwill have no impact on vehicle testing
OL,21,Fat any of its existing 15 test centres.
