OL,3,CNew MoT test centre faces further
OL,4,Cdelays
OL,6,FUTV was told by a spokesperson from
OL,7,FWorldwide Environmental Products Inc.
OL,8,Fthat the company "has commenced legal
OL,9,Fproceedings".
OL,11,FThe issue came to light at a meeting
OL,12,Fof the Infrastructure Committee on
OL,13,FWednesday.
OL,15,FThe Chair of the scrutiny committee
OL,16,FDeborah Erskine told UTV that the
OL,17,Fdevelopment was "concerning".
