OL,3,CNew MoT test centre faces further
OL,4,Cdelays
OL,6,F"There will be a long road now going
OL,7,Fforward in terms of what the next
OL,8,Fsteps will be for the department in
OL,9,Fresolving this development," she added.
OL,11,FUTV can exclusively reveal that the
OL,12,Fdepartment served a notice to
OL,13,Fterminate its contract with Worldwide
OL,14,FEnvironmental Products Inc with
OL,15,Fimmediate effect on 9th October 2024.
OL,17,FIn a statement, a spokesperson for the
OL,18,Fdepartment said a new procurement
OL,19,Fprocess is now under way which is
OL,20,Fexpected to "take a number of months".
