OL,3,CNew MoT test centre faces further
OL,4,Cdelays
OL,6,FThey added that, "regrettably, this
OL,7,Fwill further delay the opening of the
OL,8,Fnew test centre at Hydebank, Belfast,
OL,9,Ffor vehicle testing".
OL,11,FThe Department also emphasised: "This
OL,12,Fwill not impact on the provision of
OL,13,Fvehicle testing at the DVA's existing
OL,14,Fnetwork of 15 test centres, as the
OL,15,Fequipment at these test centres is
OL,16,Fprovided and maintained under a
OL,17,Fdifferent contract".
